304
00:31:14,360 --> 00:31:15,793
Let's eat.

305
00:31:33,070 --> 00:31:35,789
Nong Tian, you have a letter.

306
00:31:35,789 --> 00:31:37,060
Really?

307
00:31:37,060 --> 00:31:38,650
Thank you.

308
00:31:38,650 --> 00:31:40,160
You're welcome.

309
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:42,690
[From: Pha Pun Dao Village, Chiang Mai
To: Tian Sophaditsakul]

310
00:31:50,760 --> 00:31:53,920
[Save the Date for the Wedding of Davipa & Wasan]

311
00:32:02,390 --> 00:32:05,290
Please come to my wedding. Someone wants to see you.

312
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:19,299
Hello, Buddy.

313
00:32:19,300 --> 00:32:20,969
So, are you coming to my wedding or not?

314
00:32:20,970 --> 00:32:24,580
Doc, I'm not sure if I can make it.

315
00:32:24,580 --> 00:32:28,339
You know, I'm very busy with the wildfire training.

316
00:32:28,339 --> 00:32:32,350
Come on, I only get married once.

317
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:34,359
I don't care.

318
00:32:34,360 --> 00:32:37,869
I have reserved two seats at my wedding reception for you.

319
00:32:37,869 --> 00:32:40,240
Why two seats?

320
00:32:41,470 --> 00:32:44,069
For you and your volunteer teacher.

321
00:32:44,070 --> 00:32:45,489
I sent an invitation to him, too.

322
00:32:45,490 --> 00:32:48,740
Dress yourself up and come to my wedding.

323
00:32:50,510 --> 00:32:53,339
Doc, I've got to go now.

324
00:32:53,339 --> 00:32:55,150
I have work to do.

325
00:32:57,290 --> 00:32:58,823
Hello.

326
00:33:26,810 --> 00:33:28,860
Wow.

327
00:33:28,860 --> 00:33:31,429
You are all dressed up. What is it for, dear?

328
00:33:31,430 --> 00:33:32,969
Just once in a while, Mom.

329
00:33:32,970 --> 00:33:35,820
It's for the wedding of a senior I met at the village.

330
00:34:01,040 --> 00:34:03,190
Come here. Let me help.

331
00:34:03,190 --> 00:34:04,860
Thanks.

332
00:34:06,320 --> 00:34:08,190
Wow.

333
00:34:10,970 --> 00:34:14,829
You even put on a tailored suit.

334
00:34:14,830 --> 00:34:17,180
Are you having a date with someone?

335
00:34:18,930 --> 00:34:21,889
No. Do I look good yet?

336
00:34:21,890 --> 00:34:24,490
You do, dear. Let me button this up.

337
00:34:26,420 --> 00:34:29,309
Since you came back, I hardly see you go out.

338
00:34:29,310 --> 00:34:32,510
Today's event must be very special.

339
00:34:34,230 --> 00:34:35,809
Yes.

340
00:34:35,810 --> 00:34:37,649
You look gorgeous.

341
00:34:37,650 --> 00:34:39,600
Let me have a look again.

342
00:34:53,910 --> 00:34:55,860
You're good to go now.

343
00:35:01,390 --> 00:35:04,219
Khao Fang, let's have a photo. Come on.

344
00:35:07,320 --> 00:35:10,170
You look so beautiful today.

345
00:35:10,170 --> 00:35:13,080
[J & N]

346
00:35:29,460 --> 00:35:33,460
Wow, the wedding is so beautiful.

347
00:35:35,920 --> 00:35:38,120
You said you weren't coming.

348
00:35:38,790 --> 00:35:41,810
Good evening, everyone.

349
00:35:43,190 --> 00:35:46,989
Wow, have you seen my big beast friend?

350
00:35:46,990 --> 00:35:49,939
Doc, stop talking. Are you going to take a picture now or not?

351
00:35:49,940 --> 00:35:53,890
Of course, since you're all dressed up like this.

352
00:35:53,890 --> 00:35:55,869
Do you want to have a picture with me or…

353
00:35:55,870 --> 00:35:57,509
Someone else?

354
00:35:57,510 --> 00:35:59,639
If you don't want a picture, I'll leave.

355
00:35:59,640 --> 00:36:01,519
Wait, Chief.

356
00:36:01,520 --> 00:36:03,979
Don't make this go in vain.

357
00:36:03,979 --> 00:36:06,559
- We rented these suits from the market.
- That's right.

358
00:36:06,559 --> 00:36:08,189
I spent almost all of my salary on this.

359
00:36:08,189 --> 00:36:11,290
I'm all ready to work my flirting skills here.

360
00:36:12,010 --> 00:36:13,779
What's the rush?

361
00:36:13,780 --> 00:36:15,789
He's not here yet.

362
00:36:15,790 --> 00:36:17,879
Don't you want to see him?

363
00:36:17,880 --> 00:36:19,980
I'm here for your wedding.

364
00:36:21,350 --> 00:36:22,459
Well then, let's take a picture.

365
00:36:22,459 --> 00:36:24,169
Come on, let's take a picture.

366
00:36:24,170 --> 00:36:28,160
Make us look good in the picture.

367
00:36:31,730 --> 00:36:34,060
One, two, three.

368
00:36:35,040 --> 00:36:36,810
Yeah!

369
00:37:04,250 --> 00:37:07,360
[J & N]

370
00:37:30,130 --> 00:37:31,689
Good evening.

371
00:37:31,690 --> 00:37:33,229
Thank you for coming.

372
00:37:33,229 --> 00:37:35,063
Thank you.

373
00:38:01,240 --> 00:38:02,990
Please excuse us.

374
00:38:04,510 --> 00:38:06,043
Nong Tian.

375
00:38:07,890 --> 00:38:10,110
- Good evening.
- Good evening.

376
00:38:11,090 --> 00:38:15,209
Look at you, I can't remember you as a teacher in the village anymore.

377
00:38:15,209 --> 00:38:16,869
Let's take a picture.

378
00:38:16,870 --> 00:38:17,929
Yes, Phi.

379
00:38:17,930 --> 00:38:19,980
Take a photo of us, please.

380
00:38:23,730 --> 00:38:25,363
Thank you.

381
00:38:25,990 --> 00:38:28,680
You look so handsome tonight, Phi.

382
00:38:29,780 --> 00:38:31,590
P'Aof!

383
00:38:32,680 --> 00:38:34,870
That's my senior, P'Aof. Let me go greet him.

384
00:38:34,870 --> 00:38:36,820
Let me go greet him. I'll be right back.

385
00:38:36,821 --> 00:38:39,409
- Please enjoy yourself.
- Thank you.

386
00:38:39,409 --> 00:38:40,973
P'Aof!

387
00:38:52,690 --> 00:38:54,690
Are you looking for my friend?

388
00:38:56,570 --> 00:38:57,903
Yes.

389
00:38:58,640 --> 00:39:00,720
He was here,

390
00:39:00,720 --> 00:39:04,489
but something urgent came up, so he had to leave.

391
00:39:04,490 --> 00:39:06,490
He just left a moment ago.

392
00:39:10,670 --> 00:39:14,150
What was it that was so urgent?

393
00:39:16,140 --> 00:39:17,819
I don't know what it was.

394
00:39:17,819 --> 00:39:19,653
He didn't say.

395
00:39:25,470 --> 00:39:28,970
Maybe, he doesn't want to see me.

396
00:39:29,590 --> 00:39:32,130
Come on, Tian.

397
00:39:34,690 --> 00:39:36,523
You know what?

398
00:39:36,523 --> 00:39:41,670
He told me to forget him,

399
00:39:42,520 --> 00:39:46,649
but now, I think he's probably doing the same.

400
00:39:50,290 --> 00:39:51,823
Nam.

401
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:57,399
Please excuse me,

402
00:39:57,400 --> 00:39:59,969
but can I have your number?

403
00:39:59,970 --> 00:40:03,590
You have really deactivated your Facebook.

404
00:40:03,590 --> 00:40:05,489
Can I? Just in case.

405
00:40:05,490 --> 00:40:07,123
Absolutely.

406
00:40:10,410 --> 00:40:11,840
Okay.

407
00:40:11,840 --> 00:40:15,600
Thank you so much for coming.

408
00:40:18,210 --> 00:40:20,310
Congratulations, Phi.

409
00:40:23,980 --> 00:40:25,910
Good evening.

410
00:40:32,150 --> 00:40:34,099
Hey!

411
00:40:34,100 --> 00:40:36,060
Mr. Tian!

412
00:40:37,770 --> 00:40:39,669
I didn't expect to see you here.

413
00:40:39,670 --> 00:40:41,999
Good evening, you guys.

