481
00:47:26,430 --> 00:47:28,430
What else were you thinking of?

482
00:48:03,530 --> 00:48:06,470
[International Departures]

483
00:48:10,620 --> 00:48:12,153
Ai Tian!

484
00:48:13,170 --> 00:48:14,979
Good morning.

485
00:48:14,980 --> 00:48:16,780
What's up, buddy?

486
00:48:18,670 --> 00:48:21,120
Why do you look disappointed to see me?

487
00:48:22,160 --> 00:48:23,269
Don't be an ass here.

488
00:48:23,270 --> 00:48:25,299
Stop getting on my nerves for once. I'm leaving soon.

489
00:48:25,299 --> 00:48:29,650
