490
00:48:30,550 --> 00:48:32,159
Thanks.

491
00:48:32,159 --> 00:48:33,893
Give me a hug.

492
00:48:35,660 --> 00:48:37,539
Good luck, man.

493
00:48:37,539 --> 00:48:39,819
Don't be so hard on yourself while you're over there.

494
00:48:39,820 --> 00:48:41,719
I'm sure there are plenty of handsome men for you to choose.

495
00:48:41,719 --> 00:48:43,653
Damn it, Tul!

496
00:48:48,410 --> 00:48:50,690
What's wrong?

497
00:48:51,260 --> 00:48:53,910
You are the one who's sending him away.

498
00:48:53,910 --> 00:48:55,710
I know.

499
00:48:56,480 --> 00:48:58,420
Tian.

500
00:49:04,140 --> 00:49:06,039
Have a safe trip, dear.

501
00:49:06,039 --> 00:49:08,280
Take care of yourself.

502
00:49:13,660 --> 00:49:15,939
Take care of yourself, too.

503
00:49:15,940 --> 00:49:20,360
You, too. Do call me every day.

504
00:49:20,950 --> 00:49:23,939
Okay, I will call until you're sick of me.

505
00:49:23,939 --> 00:49:26,590
I will never get sick of you.

506
00:49:29,940 --> 00:49:32,960
Safe trip, Dear.

507
00:49:38,210 --> 00:49:40,409
Take care of yourself, Son,

508
00:49:40,409 --> 00:49:42,260
and have a safe trip.

509
00:49:43,440 --> 00:49:45,173
Thank you, Dad.

510
00:49:49,940 --> 00:49:52,240
Take care of yourself, too.

511
00:50:26,040 --> 00:50:27,673
Dad,

512
00:50:29,150 --> 00:50:31,000
I'll go inside now.

513
00:50:32,250 --> 00:50:33,569
See you, man.

514
00:50:33,570 --> 00:50:34,939
See you.

515
00:50:34,939 --> 00:50:36,940
All right, Dad. Mom.

516
00:50:36,940 --> 00:50:38,593
Goodbye.

517
00:51:06,130 --> 00:51:07,663
Hello.

518
00:51:13,060 --> 00:51:14,593
Tian.

519
00:51:22,360 --> 00:51:23,893
Chief.

520
00:51:29,660 --> 00:51:31,393
Good luck.

521
00:51:44,830 --> 00:51:46,563
Chief,

522
00:51:48,240 --> 00:51:50,770
is that all you've got to say to me?

523
00:51:56,920 --> 00:51:58,753
I miss you.

524
00:52:49,500 --> 00:52:51,400
I want to send you off.

525
00:53:03,180 --> 00:53:05,570
Why are you so hard to please?

526
00:53:08,380 --> 00:53:12,490
If you do this, how could I ever forget you?

527
00:53:16,450 --> 00:53:18,690
Do you think I could?

528
00:53:19,910 --> 00:53:23,010
Can you forget about what I asked you to forget?

529
00:53:26,040 --> 00:53:28,340
What exactly do you want, Chief?

530
00:53:29,540 --> 00:53:31,509
Will you change your mind again later?

531
00:53:31,510 --> 00:53:33,043
Hm?

532
00:53:35,330 --> 00:53:37,380
